{"tid":1993072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"荷蘭駐台機構更名 中國提出嚴正交涉","createTime":"2020-04-28T13:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T14:19:47.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f32d6e998337d761c1de703787da50289ae9074c","tid":1993072,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"荷蘭貿易暨投資辦事處代表紀維德(Guy Wittich)本週一宣佈，該處的名稱簡化為&ldquo;荷蘭在台辦事處&rdquo;，並形容這樣的更名是&ldquo;少一點，多很多&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n對此，中國官媒《環球時報》報導，中國駐荷蘭大使館表達了嚴重關切，隨即與荷蘭外交部聯繫，要求荷方澄清，並提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n報導還說，台灣問題涉及中方核心利益，堅持&ldquo;一中原則&rdquo;是發展中荷關係的政治基礎。<br />\n<br />\n新冠疫情持續蔓延全球之際，台灣日前捐贈荷蘭60萬片口罩，荷蘭外交官員回函表示感謝，並肯定台灣成功控制疫情，也將學習相關經驗。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，荷蘭衛生部表示，已經召回60萬片從中國進口的口罩，理由是這些口罩的質量未達標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/netherlands-and-taiwan-ties-20200428/5395296.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fnetherlands-and-taiwan-ties-20200428%2F5395296.html&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ee628b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/netherlands-and-taiwan-ties-20200428/5395296.html</a>"},{"pid":"53b5c0b8521c4189044d8d008337c7c82d910e0b","tid":1993072,"uid":157987,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲夠膽攞啲唔及格既口罩出黎講 唔講荷蘭都冇咁嬲 回左水未"},{"pid":"08e28b41021ef72dd64bc3bbda8c668e4bd0aa76","tid":1993072,"uid":271211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T13:43:40.000Z","msg":"全世界都知台灣係一個國家<br />\n係得中國唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ffaa419e897c382915a6b89d1dcee0fef1ebcd","tid":1993072,"uid":144811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"中華民國(在台灣)立國仲早過共匪國！"},{"pid":"4a4169865d17ebeddab1d8c8e9715f9bd5436a93","tid":1993072,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p